ZH: 不经意间我听到了他们的谈话。
EN: I overheard their conversation by accident.

ZH: 我不经意间把你的包放在了这张椅子上。
EN: I put your bag on this chair unintentionally.

ZH: 她不经意间打翻了一杯咖啡。
EN: She accidentally spilled a cup of coffee.

ZH: 我们不经意间穿错了鞋子。
EN: We mistakenly wore the wrong shoes.

ZH: 他不经意间碰到了她的手。
EN: He inadvertently touched her hand.

ZH: 她在不经意间笑了起来。
EN: She laughed spontaneously.

ZH: 我不经意间迟到了五分钟。
EN: I unintentionally arrived five minutes late.

ZH: 他不经意间踩到了一滩水。
EN: He accidentally stepped on a puddle of water.

ZH: 我们不经意间走错了路。
EN: We mistakenly took the wrong path.

ZH: 他不经意间撞到了一个陌生人。
EN: He inadvertently bumped into a stranger.

ZH: 不经意间，我发现了一本老书。
EN: By chance, I discovered an old book.

ZH: 她不经意间发现了我藏在抽屉里的信件。
EN: She came across the letters I kept in the drawer unexpectedly.

ZH: 我们不经意间遇到了一个年份。
EN: We stumbled upon a vintage item by accident.

ZH: 他不经意间做出了一个正确的决定。
EN: He unknowingly made a wise decision.

